00149   class PDB_residues{
00150   public:
00152     static const pdb_atom_info_t*
00153     get_atom_info(const std::string atom_str, const std::string res_str)
00154     {
00155       if(!residue_table.size()) PDB_residues::build_res_tables();
00156       atom_table_t::const_iterator a_iter = residue_table.find(atom_str);
00157       if(a_iter == residue_table.end()) return 0;
00158       str_tbl_res_lvl::const_iterator res_iter = a_iter->second.find(res_str);
00159       if(res_iter == a_iter->second.end()) return 0;
00160       return res_iter->second;
00161     }
00162 
00164     static const pdb_atom_info_t*
00165     get_atom_info(const atom_type atom, residue_type residue)
00166     {
00167       if(!residue_type_table.size()) PDB_residues::build_res_tables();
00168       atom_enum_table_t::const_iterator a_iter = residue_type_table.find(atom);
00169       if(a_iter == residue_type_table.end()) return 0;
00170       enum_tbl_res_lvl::const_iterator res_iter = a_iter->second.find(residue);
00171       if(res_iter == a_iter->second.end()) return 0;
00172       return res_iter->second;
00173     }
00174 
00175     static int
00176     get_atom_hydrophobicity(const residue_type res, const atom_type atom)
00177     {
00178       if(A_hydrophobic_value.size() == 0) build_atom_hphob_map();
00179 
00180       // Default value for oxygen is 530 - 235
00181       if(atom == OXT) return 295; 
00182       hphob_tbl_res_lvl::const_iterator res_iter;
00183       res_iter = A_hydrophobic_value.find(res);
00184       if(res_iter == A_hydrophobic_value.end()) 
00185         return std::numeric_limits<int>::max();
00186       hphob_tbl_atom_lvl::const_iterator a_iter;
00187       a_iter = res_iter->second.find(atom);
00188       if(a_iter == res_iter->second.end())
00189         return std::numeric_limits<int>::max();
00190       return a_iter->second;
00191     }
